Project overview 
The PowerFlex API provides unified, secure, and consistent access to manage storage infrastructure through automation, enabling integration with DevOps tools and workflows.

Audience
The audience for the PowerFlex API is develoeprs and customers who are using the PowerFlex Block REST API to deploy block storage on PowerFlex nodes and the PowerFlex Manager REST API to manage and orchestrate their PowerFlex Nodes.

